Hi Team,
&nbsp;
The customer sells perfumes and would like to display the SKU code on the Amazon Shipping label instead of the full product name. Since the product name is currently visible on the label, delivery personnel can easily identify the contents of the package. The customer has reported that package thefts have already occurred and believes the visibility of the product name is contributing to the issue.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
To help prevent further incidents, they would like the label to display only the SKU and quantity instead of the Product name or description.
&nbsp;
Please provide this option ASAP.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
(Abhilash)
&nbsp;

L3 - Please enable the toggle feature to show the SKU and Quantity of the product on the Amazon Shipping labels for below mentioned store
&nbsp;
Store URL - 948165-59.myshopify.com&nbsp;
Account ID - 6bab6a3b-6770-4fbd-8d0f-35cb81352953

Customer Requirement - To show SKU and Quantity instead of product name on the Amazon Shipping labels
&nbsp;
Abhilash will be check about this with Vimal sir

Hi Lakshya,
&nbsp;
Please allow me some time to check this with our technical team.
&nbsp;
In the meantime, could you please share an order ID that we can use to generate a test label and verify the behavior on our end?
If you'd like, we can also cancel the label after the test is completed.
&nbsp;
Once I hear back from our technical team, I will provide you with an update.
&nbsp;
Best regards,
Priyanka
Team PluginHive

